definition: to sign one's name/visa/variant of 籤|签[qian1]
inscribed bamboo stick (used in divination, gambling, drawing lots etc)/small wood sliver/label/tag
to enter/to go into/to join/to become a member of/to confirm or agree with/abbr. for 入聲|入声[ru4 sheng1]

sentences.chinese: 将签入说明与变更集相关联。

sentences.english: Test lists are used as a part of check-in policy.
sentences.chinese: 将测试列表用作签入策略的一部分。

sentences.english: However, Gill says the Reds turned down the opportunity to sign Mascherano.
sentences.chinese: 不过，吉尔说曼联放弃了签入马斯切拉诺的机会。

sentences.english: This error arises when a change is made to a file that is currently checked in to source-code control.
sentences.chinese: 当更改当前签入到源代码控件的文件时，出现此错误。

sentences.english: It assumes you are checking-in code at least once a day.
sentences.chinese: 它认为每天只要至少签入一次代码即可。

sentences.english: 'It's been incredibly hard to sign players' By Nick Teale Arsène Wenger admits it has been "incredibly difficult" to sign players this summer.
sentences.chinese: 温格承认这个夏天签入球员的困难程度让人难以想象。

sentences.english: He plays Newcastle on Sunday August 14, but he can sign players until August 31.
sentences.chinese: 即使赛季开始，温格还是可以签入新的球员的。

sentences.english: E-mail is delivered to team members who have subscribed for check-in notification.
sentences.chinese: 向那些订阅了签入通知的团队成员发送电子邮件。

sentences.english: Associate or resolve work items with the changeset during the check-in process.
sentences.chinese: 进行签入程序时，关联或解决工作项目与变更集。

sentences.english: If a user attempts to perform a check-in, in violation of a policy, their check-in is blocked.
sentences.chinese: 如果用户尝试违反策略执行签入，则阻止其签入。

sentences.english: If a user attempts to perform a check-in, in violation of a policy, their check-in is blocked.
sentences.chinese: 如果用户尝试违反策略执行签入，则阻止其签入。

sentences.english: Yes, we've already put name tags on our suitcases.
sentences.chinese: 是的，我们已经把名签入到了小提箱上。

sentences.english: Not all files in the pending check-in are within the currently open solution.
sentences.chinese: 挂起签入中的某些文件不属于当前打开的解决方案。

sentences.english: Inter Milan coach Roberto Mancini has ruled out signing Lazio wing-back Cesar this month.
sentences.chinese: 国米教练曼齐尼已经取消了在本月签入塞萨尔的计划。

sentences.english: Using the Check In and Pending Changes Windows.
sentences.chinese: 使用“签入”和“挂起的更改”窗口。
